## PHASE 3 — KLIP-SELECTOR (CSV FIRST, SCRAPERS SECOND)

Phase 3 v1 uses a CSV of manually curated products. Scrapers are Phase 3 v2.

`products.csv` format:
```
url,category,commission_rate,asin,title
https://amzn.to/...,beauty,8.0,B08XYZ123,Face Serum...
```

`klip-selector/selector_worker.py`:
```python
def run_cycle(limit=5):
    products = manual_feeder.load()                     # reads products.csv
    products = [p for p in products if uae_filter.passes(p)]
    products = sorted(products, key=scorer.score, reverse=True)
    top = products[:limit]
    for p in top:
        if is_blacklisted(p["url"]):
            continue
        p["layout"] = layout_router.route(p["category"])
        p["avatar_id"] = os.getenv("ACTIVE_AVATAR_ID", "theanikaglow")
        job_id = f"{int(time.time())}_{abs(hash(p['url']))%10000:04d}"
        Redis.from_env().lpush("klip:jobs:pending", json.dumps({
            "job_id": job_id, **p, "retry_count": 0
        }))
        print(f"[SELECTOR] Queued {job_id}: {p['title'][:60]}", flush=True)
```

**Validation gate:** `python klip-selector/selector_worker.py` → 5 jobs in Upstash queue → all process automatically → 5 videos in HITL.

